Icon Libraries:

- Always prefer Material Design Icons (@mdi/react + @mdi/js) for icon usage
- Import icons from @mdi/js: `import { mdiIconName } from '@mdi/js'`
- Use Icon component from @mdi/react: `import Icon from '@mdi/react'`
- Example usage: `<Icon path={mdiIconName} size={1} />`
- Browse icons at: <https://pictogrammers.com/library/mdi/>
- Icon names use PascalCase with 'mdi' prefix (e.g., 'arrow-left' â†’ `mdiArrowLeft`)
- Only import icons you need (tree-shakeable)
- Fallback to lucide-react only if MDI doesn't have the needed icon
